    "This limited number of articles as illustrated in Fig. 3a indicates that this topic is still in its infancy and rather underrepresented compared to the application of blockchain in other fields such as healthcare, IoT, and supply chain management [13,14,42].Through this study, we have identified 10 different application areas of blockchain in the sports industry as shown in detail in Fig.",
